tool_description: Translates Text to mores code and mores code to Text
name: Mores Code Translator
title: Mores Code Translator

api_list.name: Convert Text To Mores Code
api_list.description: This endpoint converts Text to mores code
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://mores-code-translator.p.rapidapi.com/convert_text_to_morse/Hello"

headers = {
            "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
            "X-RapidAPI-Host": "mores-code-translator.p.rapidapi.com"
        }

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers)
print(response.json())
